---
title: Features
description: Solidus can flex, adjust and extend as you deliver your customers a personalized shopping experience all day, every day.
---

<div class="content-block-gray-100">
  <div class="features-hero features__gradient hero-block content-block--skewed">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg">
            <div class="pr-md-6 mb-3">
              <h1 class="title">Build whatever you want on top of the core.</h1>
              <p class="mb-md-6">
                Start from a strong core feature-set that will give a solid base to understand what your business really needs. Then iterate: add, remove and reuse till perfection. When you choose Solidus, you never have to change your platform again.
              </p>
              <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/contact">Get started</a>
              <a class="btn btn-secondary btn-white" href="http://solidemo.herokuapp.com/" target="_blank">Demo</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg">
            <div class="hero-image-wrapper">
              <%= inline_svg("illustrations/features-hero.svg", class: "hero-image") %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content-block">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="features__header">
            <h2>Core functionalities shaped by success.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>
            You can rely on the shared knowledge of brands that revolutionized the eCommerce world. Some of the most powerful functionalities you can find are already at your business disposal.
          </p>
          <a href="">Lorem ipsum</a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md">
          <%= inline_svg("illustrations/features-brands.svg", class: "img-fluid") %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content-block features__gradient text-center">
    <div class="container container-md">
      <div class="features__header">
        <h2 class="title">All the features.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="lead">
        Solidus offers essential ecommerce features out of the box. Take what you need, leave what you don’t, then fine-tune the rest to meet the needs of your store
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="sub-navbar">
    <div class="container container-md">
      <ul class="nav justify-content-around align-items-center">
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#product">Product</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#flexibility">Flexibility</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#payment">Payment</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#shipping">Shipping</a></li>
        <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#customers">Customers</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features content-block" id="product">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><%= inline_svg("icons/product.svg", class: "isvg group") %> Product</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md order-md-2 mb-5">
          <img src="<%= image_path("illustrations/features-product@1x.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("illustrations/features-product@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("illustrations/features-product@1x.png") %> 1x" class="img-fluid" width="100%" alt="Product" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="mb-5">
            <h4>Inventory management</h4>
            <p>Manage your incoming and outgoing inventory across multiple warehouses and storefronts. It’s easy to update and monitor your product stock as your business grows.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <h4>Product management</h4>
            <p>Add products and create variants based on product attributes or user-collected data. Create searchable product lists. Even add metadata to products such as a manufacturer number.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-5">
            <h4>Taxonomy management</h4>
            <p>Organize your products using custom categories and subcategories. Give your categories customer-friendly names on the front-end. Your products can belong to any number of categories.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features content-block--skewed content-block-gray-900" id="flexibility">
    <div class="features__flexibility container content-wrapper">
      <h2><%= inline_svg("icons/flexibility.svg", class: "isvg group") %> Flexibility</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-8">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md mb-5">
              <h4>Restful API</h4>
              <p>Add products and create variants based on product attributes or user-collected data. Create searchable product lists. Even add metadata to products such as a manufacturer number.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md mb-5">
              <h4>Product management</h4>
              <p>Add products and create variants based on product attributes or user-collected data. Create searchable product lists. Even add metadata to products such as a manufacturer number.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <h4>Taxonomy management</h4>
              <p>Organize your products using custom categories and subcategories. Give your categories customer-friendly names on the front-end. Your products can belong to any number of categories.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features content-block" id="payment">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><%= inline_svg("icons/payments.svg", class: "isvg group") %> Payment</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
          <img class="mb-5" src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-tax_placeholder@2x.png') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-tax.svg') %>" alt="Tax calculation" height="178" width="auto">
          <h4>Tax calculation</h4>
          <p>Calculate taxes for each country, state, or custom zone that you ship to. The built-in tax calculator is flexible and extensible, which means that it can handle all your complex rates and tax categories.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
          <img class="mb-5" src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-payment_placeholder@2x.png') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-payment.svg') %>" alt="Payment integrations" height="178" width="auto">
          <h4>Payment integrations</h4>
          <p>Add products and create variants based on product attributes or user-collected data. Create searchable product lists. Even add metadata to products such as a manufacturer number.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
          <img class="mb-5" src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-promotions_placeholder@2x.png') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-promotions.svg') %>" alt="Promotions" height="178" width="auto">
          <h4>Promotions</h4>
          <p>Organize your products using custom categories and subcategories. Give your categories customer-friendly names on the front-end. Your products can belong to any number of categories.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 offset-lg-2 mb-5">
          <img class="mb-5 mt-md-5" src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-subscription_placeholder@2x.png') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-subscription.svg') %>" alt="Subscription support" height="178" width="auto">
          <h4>Subscription support</h4>
          <p>Manage your incoming and outgoing inventory across multiple warehouses and storefronts. It’s easy to update and monitor your product stock as your business grows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <img class="mb-5 mt-md-5" src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-store-credit_placeholder@2x.png') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-store-credit.svg') %>" alt="Store credit" height="178" width="auto">
          <h4>Store credit</h4>
          <p>Add products and create variants based on product attributes or user-collected data. Create searchable product lists. Even add metadata to products such as a manufacturer number.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="features content-block--skewed content-block-gray-900" id="shipping">
    <div class="features__shipping container content-wrapper">
      <h2><%= inline_svg("icons/shipping.svg", class: "isvg group") %> Shipping</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-8">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md mb-5">
              <h4>Order Managment</h4>
              <p>Streamline your order fulfillment. See customer carts, shipments, promotions, returns and payment information in one location. Easily resend purchase or shipping confirmation emails or make payment adjustments after a sale.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md mb-5">
              <h4>Multi-carrier Shipping</h4>
              <p>Provide multiple shipping options at checkout. Offer free shipping, flat- or percentage-based rates. Buy postage, request real-time carrier rates and shop around with shipping extensions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4">
              <h4>Return and exchanges</h4>
              <p>Make returns and exchanges hassle-free for your customers as well as your customer service team. Manage every aspect of these transactions and keep them clearly documented.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="features content-block" id="customers">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><%= inline_svg("icons/customers.svg", class: "isvg group") %> Customers</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md order-md-2 mb-5">
          <img src="<%= image_path("illustrations/features-customers@1x.png") %>" data-srcset="<%= image_path("illustrations/features-customers@2x.png") %> 2x, <%= image_path("illustrations/features-customers@1x.png") %> 1x" class="img-fluid" width="100%" alt="Customers" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md">
          <div class="mb-5">
            <h4>User permissions</h4>
            <p>Limit access to any part of the Solidus admin interface. Create and assign multiple roles for each user. Restrict sales data, site settings or editing functionality for any section individually.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4>Customer management</h4>
            <p>View your customers’ lifetime stats – including their total number of orders, address changes, store credit amount and more.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content-block content-block-white">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md">
          <h2>All the freedom.</h2>
          <p>Limit access to any part of the Solidus admin interface. Create and assign multiple roles for each user. Restrict sales data, site settings or editing functionality for any section individually.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md mt-5 mt-sm-0">
          <img class="img-fluid" src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-all-the-freedom_placeholder@2x.png') %>" data-src="<%= image_path('illustrations/features-all-the-freedom.svg') %>" alt="All the freedom">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="features">
    <%= partial "partials/cta_bottom" %>
  </div>
</div>
